<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BBC News</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        /* Header Styles */
        .header {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .header-logo {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .header-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .header-auth {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        /* Navigation Styles */
        .navigation {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .navigation-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        /* Main Content Styles */
        .main-content {
            padding: 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 3fr 2fr;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .news-item {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .news-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .news-item h2 {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .news-item p {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
        }

        .news-item .details {
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #888;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-logo">BBC</div>
        <div class="header-links">
            <span>News</span>
            <span>Sport</span>
            <span>Business</span>
            <span>Innovation</span>
            <span>Culture</span>
            <span>Arts</span>
            <span>Travel</span>
            <span>Earth</span>
            <span>Audio</span>
            <span>Video</span>
            <span>Live</span>
        </div>
        <div class="header-auth">
            <button>Register</button>
            <button>Sign In</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="navigation">
        <div class="navigation-links">
            <span>Home</span>
            <span>News</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="news-item">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/400x225" alt="News Image">
            <h2>Trump says he is 'not happy' with deadly Russian strikes on Kyiv</h2>
            <p>The overnight strikes killed at least 12 people and injured 90 more, local officials have said.</p>
            <div class="details">2 hrs ago | World</div>
        </div>

        <div class="news-item">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/600x340" alt="News Image">
            <h2>News Headline Example</h2>
            <p>This is a brief summary of the news article. It provides a quick overview of the main points.</p>
            <div class="details">1 hr ago | Local</div>
        </div>

        <div class="news-item">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/400x225" alt="News Image">
            <h2>Pakistan suspends visas for Indians after deadly Kashmir attack on tourists</h2>
            <p>It comes after Delhi's retaliatory measures following a militant attack in Indian-administered Kashmir that killed 26 tourists.</p>
            <div class="details">16 hrs ago | Asia</div>
        </div>

        <div class="news-item">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/400x225" alt="News Image">
            <h2>I'm alive but three in my group didn't make it' - Kashmir attack survivor</h2>
            <p>Tourists are returning home after a deadly gun attack killed 26 visitors in Indian-administered Kashmir.</p>
            <div class="details">2 hrs ago | Asia</div>
        </div>

         <div class="news-item">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/400x225" alt="News Image">
            <h2>California passes Japan as fourth largest economy</h2>
            <p>The US state expresses worries that President Donald Trump's tariffs could stunt future growth.</p>
            <div class="details">3 hrs ago | World</div>
        </div>

        <div class="news-item">
            <img src="https://placehold.co/400x225" alt="News Image">
            <h2>Mass food poisonings cast shadow over Indonesia's free school meals</h2>
            <p>Nearly 80 students across two high schools fell sick after eating the meals this week.</p>
            <div class="details">7 hrs ago | Asia</div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
